htungen? Der Band versammelt hierzu Beiträge führender Persönlichkeiten aus der Museums- und Kulturlandschaft, die aus unterschiedlichen Blickwinkeln zukunftsweisende Methoden und Ansätze für die Arbeit in Museen aufzeigen.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 4aCultural Entrepreneurship. 4aCultural Leadership. 4aDesign Thinking. 4aInnovation. 4aKultur. 4aKulturelle Bildung. 4aKulturmanagement. 4aKünstliche Intelligenz. 4aMuseum. 4aMuseumsmanagement. 4aMuseumspädagogik. 7aART / Museum Studies.2bisacsh  aArtificial Intelligence.  aCultural Education.  aCultural Entrepreneurship.  aCultural Management.  aCulture.  aDesign Thinking.  aInnovation.  aMuseum Education.  aMuseum Management.  aMuseum.1 aAllmanritter, Vera, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBauernfeind, Judith, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBeaury, Paul, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBirnkraut, Gesa, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFöhl, Patrick S., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGeipel, Andrea, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGerjets, Peter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGreve, Anna, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHohmann, Georg, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHoins, Katharina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKlein, Armin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKonrad, Elmar D., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLandau-Donnelly, Friederike, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb